one and so cohort is just a group of players that share some characteristics.

238
00:12:04,725 --> 00:12:07,066
So it's a subset of all the players

239
00:12:07,126 --> 00:12:08,827
and they share some characteristic together.

240
00:12:09,328 --> 00:12:13,250
And this card has significantly better ARPU,

