So town in Guild Wars 2 are no combat social hubs in the game.

249
00:12:39,266 --> 00:12:43,208
Now, it's not as if you really need to spend time in town

250
00:12:43,408 --> 00:12:44,208
in Guild Wars 2.

251
00:12:45,408 --> 00:12:47,289
In fact, there's exceedingly little

252
00:12:47,749 --> 00:12:49,770
that actually requires you to return to town.

253
00:12:50,750 --> 00:12:55,511
The spending money on microtransactions,

254
