00:19:00,861 --> 00:19:03,061
It would not be super fair for me to come and say,

390
00:19:03,422 --> 00:19:05,422
hey, LiveOps is great, it's so much better

391
00:19:05,742 --> 00:19:07,083
than all these other things you're doing,

392
00:19:07,343 --> 00:19:09,243
and then not actually explain how to do it.

