00:19:10,424 --> 00:19:13,485
Well, like most things in game development, it's a journey.

394
00:19:14,396 --> 00:19:17,797
Not a destination, just like prelaunch development, right?

395
00:19:18,117 --> 00:19:24,100
LiveOps is a set of steps, so just prelaunch development,

396
00:19:24,160 --> 00:19:26,320
and this is a very simplified version of that journey,

397
00:19:26,360 --> 00:19:27,421
pre-production, production, launch.

