00:19:32,543 --> 00:19:35,284
LiveOps tends to be additive instead of sequential.

401
00:19:35,784 --> 00:19:38,445
So you never actually stop doing the basics.

402
00:19:38,902 --> 00:19:40,943
You just keep adding more and more on, right?

403
00:19:40,963 --> 00:19:43,865
So we start by doing basics, then we add optimizations,

404
00:19:43,945 --> 00:19:44,826
then we add mastery.

