00:20:04,846 --> 00:20:06,707
you should be thinking about your progression design,

416
00:20:06,727 --> 00:20:09,088
your retention design, your monetization strategy.

417
00:20:09,548 --> 00:20:12,369
Then during production, you've got to be thinking about

418
00:20:12,529 --> 00:20:13,930
what kind of goals you're going to be setting,

419
00:20:13,970 --> 00:20:16,191
what kind of data you're going to be pulling in,

420
00:20:16,531 --> 00:20:18,051
how you're going to do live content,

421
00:20:18,411 --> 00:20:20,012
how you're going to do community feedback.

422
00:20:20,112 --> 00:20:22,133
All of these things need to be part of the process

423
00:20:22,173 --> 00:20:23,013
of building your game.

424
00:20:24,014 --> 00:20:25,674
Then once you launch,

425
00:20:26,055 --> 00:20:28,416
then we start getting into the specifics of these basics.

