00:20:32,804 --> 00:20:35,325
and then adding in player behavior analytics,

429
00:20:35,365 --> 00:20:38,386
strategy adjustments, segmentation and targeting,

430
00:20:38,706 --> 00:20:39,866
breaking your game apart,

431
00:20:39,946 --> 00:20:42,747
and really looking at how different players experience it,

432
00:20:43,367 --> 00:20:46,888
all the way into community shaping, brand retention.

