00:23:46,483 --> 00:23:47,983
They really try to make the game

494
00:23:48,063 --> 00:23:50,003
as perfect as possible before shipping.

495
00:23:50,518 --> 00:23:55,499
And sometimes, inadvertently, that actually hinders their ability to iterate the game later

