00:23:59,480 --> 00:24:02,141
That might seem tautological, but if you want to iterate on your game,

498
00:24:02,421 --> 00:24:04,581
you need to design it to be iterated on.

499
00:24:04,881 --> 00:24:08,862
And that actually speaks to the architecture of your game content

500
00:24:09,123 --> 00:24:12,523
and the way that you're organizing all of what your game is.

